You have your orders, do as you're told.

22
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,363
Yes, Your Holiness.

23
00:03:02,248 --> 00:03:05,686
(dramatic music)

24
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:09,116
You are the great Governor,
I am the High Priest.

25
00:03:09,140 --> 00:03:10,926
It is urgent that we talk.

26
