28
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:19,106
Our great God Mara has been stolen.

29
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:21,470
Oh, that is bad news,
how do, you don't suppose...

30
00:03:21,494 --> 00:03:23,936
I tell you it was stolen.

31
