I know what he's talkin' about.

35
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:37,506
Those two suspicious
characters looking for Dr. Lee.

36
00:03:37,530 --> 00:03:39,936
All right, all right, I'll look into it.

37
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,586
And next time, I'll hear
more of this fine story.

38
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:45,306
You must catch these
thieves in three days,

39
00:03:45,330 --> 00:03:47,276
if you want to save Wingpoo,

40
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:50,193
or the Dragon Lady will destroy you all.

41
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,906
Now the way I see
it, it's something were

42
