Why, why should those
two little old lie,

76
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,756
although now I'm sure you can see

77
00:05:27,780 --> 00:05:30,956
for yourself why they
must be sent on home.

78
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:35,226
Wan, go into town and
find the police chief,

79
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,076
tell him to find out who's responsible

80
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:39,433
for these shenanigans and lock 'em up.

81
00:05:41,334 --> 00:05:44,296
(men yelling)

82
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,626
(gun firing)

83
