Senor Stanton, it's no good.

111
00:06:57,590 --> 00:07:00,266
Somebody tip off police,
now they go to jail.

112
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:01,836
We still got those box of bombs.

113
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:04,091
Miguel's right, it's worth a try.

114
00:07:04,115 --> 00:07:06,426
All I know is, bombs better cinch it

115
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:07,876
because fire didn't.

116
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,506
Hold it Captain, you make mistake.

117
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,676
These are our friends.

118
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:11,510
Are you kidding,

119
00:07:11,534 --> 00:07:12,976
I've never seen these
guys before in my life.

120
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,810
Have you Terry?

121
00:07:13,834 --> 00:07:15,796
No, never before now.

122
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:17,574
Come on, let's get started.

123
00:07:17,598 --> 00:07:20,348
(dramatic music)

