00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:07,377
and your homes.

135
00:08:07,401 --> 00:08:10,182
They must be punished or
Wingpoo will be destroyed.

136
00:08:10,206 --> 00:08:13,066
(men yelling)

137
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:15,940
Listen, there's only
one thing left to do

138
00:08:16,776 --> 00:08:19,440
and that's burn down the jail.

139
00:08:19,464 --> 00:08:20,678
(men yelling)

140
00:08:20,702 --> 00:08:21,702
See, let's go.

141
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,433
Gosh Pat, looks like
the whole town's outside.

142
00:08:32,136 --> 00:08:34,636
(men yelling)

143
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,730
Start diggin', right there.

144
