[Henchman] The dynamite's
in place, Mr. Stanton.

145
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,720
Okay, light it.

146
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,493
Get that window open.

147
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:10,620
Hurry!

148
