(building exploding)

149
00:09:30,490 --> 00:09:33,496
Well, that settles it.

150
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:35,243
Now we can go finish our plans.

151
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:39,516
You two stand guard out here.

152
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,990
Remember, keep your guard up.

153
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,373
You stand guard first, me do.

154
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:48,726
I'm sure glad to see you alive.

155
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:50,266
I'm afraid, I wasn't much help.

156
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:51,576
You did more than enough.

157
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,409
Thanks for everything.

158
00:09:52,433 --> 00:09:53,433
Sit down.

159
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:55,246
Now what happened?

160
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:56,080
We were ambushed.

161
00:09:56,104 --> 00:09:58,206
Chased us, all the
way down to the river.

162
00:09:58,230 --> 00:09:59,427
And Pat and I swam...

