00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,113
Dow, that will be all.

165
00:10:05,050 --> 00:10:07,056
He might be one of them.

166
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,216
Now, go ahead.

167
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,050
Anyway...

168
00:10:09,074 --> 00:10:10,276
Hold it Terry.

169
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:11,496
You know, we explained to those people,

170
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,646
we were just scientists.

171
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:14,726
The problem is, why were
they trying to kill us?

172
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:16,506
I think I know.

173
00:10:16,530 --> 00:10:17,716
A statue of some kind,

174
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:20,376
might have been stolen from
the Dragon Lady's temple.

175
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,156
They think you're responsible.

176
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,646
Well that's it then.

177
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:25,876
We were there, when the real
thieves made away with it.

178
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:27,276
But we had nothing to do with the plan.

179
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:28,846
However, the villagers now believe

180
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,606
that you are the ones who are to blame.

181
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,996
Maybe Fang's men stole it.

182
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:34,516
I bet I know where it is,
same place he took Normandie.

183
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:36,786
Let's just go to the temple and
tell her that's where it is.

184
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:38,706
You're right, it's worth a try.

185
00:10:38,730 --> 00:10:40,016
Whatever you want.

186
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,616
I want to help you with
everything, is there any way I can?

187
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,547
I don't know.

188
00:10:43,571 --> 00:10:45,936
That would be putting you and
your daughter in great danger.

189
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,896
Would it be asking too much for a shower?

190
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:48,729
Of course not.

191
00:10:48,753 --> 00:10:49,562
Make yourselves at home.

192
00:10:49,586 --> 00:10:50,395
- Please.
- Thanks.

193
00:10:50,419 --> 00:10:51,419
Come on Terry.

194
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:57,637
He said, "Keep up your guard."

195
00:10:58,710 --> 00:11:01,603
You no worry, I keep
it with me, I worry.

196
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:04,630
Take this away.

197
00:11:07,490 --> 00:11:09,116
Well, better get going.

198
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:10,016
Better take my pistol.

199
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:10,849
Smart.

200
00:11:10,873 --> 00:11:11,786
And a couple of rifles.

201
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:12,620
I'll get them.

202
