205
00:11:15,810 --> 00:11:17,706
[Mr. Drake] I hope to
get it back in one piece.

206
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:19,216
Watch out for Fang's men.

207
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,050
That'll be swell.

208
00:11:20,074 --> 00:11:21,410
I'll be back in a minute.

209
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,696
Goodbye boys, you should be careful.

210
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,853
Are you safe here?

211
