216
00:11:52,458 --> 00:11:53,268
(drums beating)

217
00:11:53,292 --> 00:11:55,136
Stop, what do you think you're doing?

218
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,326
You're one of Fang's men.

219
00:11:56,350 --> 00:11:58,834
You'll get it when my
father finds out about this.

220
00:11:58,858 --> 00:12:01,608
(dramatic music)

221
00:12:06,964 --> 00:12:09,631
(drums beating)

222
00:12:19,673 --> 00:12:21,466
(drums beating)

223
00:12:21,490 --> 00:12:22,516
Message all right.

224
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:25,874
Me go back to house,
before Master Drake find out.

225
00:12:25,898 --> 00:12:28,648
(dramatic music)

226
00:12:32,580 --> 00:12:33,586
Master Fang, Master Fang.

227
00:12:33,610 --> 00:12:36,566
Message from Wingpoo,
saying two white men gone,

228
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:38,556
know all about statue.

229
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:40,876
Two men gone to Dragon Lady's temple.

230
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:42,216
The fools.

231
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,676
Stanton has failed.

232
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,746
They must be stopped, await my orders.

233
00:12:45,770 --> 00:12:46,926
Now go!

234
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:49,876
Dr. Lee, it seems our
conversation has been cut short,

235
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:51,226
due to outside affairs.

236
00:12:51,250 --> 00:12:52,646
However, we shall talk again.

237
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:53,670
Take him away.

238
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:02,876
Go into the jungle, find these men,

239
00:13:02,900 --> 00:13:05,036
before they reach the Temple of the Dawn.

240
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:07,116
Remember, they must be
stopped at all costs.

241
00:13:07,140 --> 00:13:08,986
Yes, Master Fang.

242
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:10,566
Ambo and I shall do your bidding.

243
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:13,097
See that you do, now hurry, hurry.

244
00:13:18,464 --> 00:13:19,464
Ambo!

245
