251
00:14:35,836 --> 00:14:37,056
Normandie, where have you been?

252
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,156
I was worried about you.

253
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:40,246
Oh, I'm sorry dad, but
I was suspicious of Dow,

254
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:41,080
so I followed him.

255
00:14:41,104 --> 00:14:42,696
