A message to Fang, telling
him all about our plans.

257
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,996
It's been hours, they're far away

258
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:48,746
but we have to try and warn them.

259
00:14:48,770 --> 00:14:50,033
We have to do something.

260
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,406
There's only one choice, I have to,

261
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:54,113
oh, oh my shoulder.

